name: Juliette Bain
bio:
.::.COCKY.::. If I ain't LABELED DA SHIT den who is? Get like me...

I'm very reserved 2 strangers. 
Love tellin jokes n makin' fun of ppl. 
Hate b n screamed at. 
I'm not friendly. 
I give great advice 2ward any situation but its hard 2 listen 2 my own advice when it comes 2 me. 
I neva been conceited just confident.
I'm sweet just until u try me.  
I DISLIKE HOES. HOES DISLIKE ME. 
Very sexy but yall know dat. 
I try not 2 b a fighter, but I'm really a lover. 
Talk shit 2 me, Ima talk shit 2 u. 
Not 1 4 drama but if it come my way shits finna get handled....
